com.adobe.creativesdk.foundation.storage

Class AdobeLibraryComposite

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.adobe.creativesdk.foundation.storage.AdobeLibraryComposite

  • public class AdobeLibraryComposite
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a single library. Use this class to add/remove/browse elements, to add/remove/browse representations, and to get/set renditions of elements (i.e. thumbnails) in a library.

    Library creation and deletion should be done via AdobeLibraryManager.

      • getRenditionPath

        public boolean getRenditionPath(java.lang.String elementId,
                                int size,
                                boolean fullSize,
                                IAdobeGenericCompletionCallback<java.lang.String> completionCallback,
                                IAdobeGenericErrorCallback<AdobeLibraryException> errorCallback,
                                android.os.Handler callbackHandler)
        Gets the path to an element's rendition for a particular size. This method will return a rendition in the following order:
        1. First check the local cache for a rendition of the requested size.
        2. Next it will check for a representation that has been marked as a rendition with the given size.
        3. After it will find any representation that can be used to generate a rendition and generate one using Adobe's imaging service.
        4. Returns false if all the above methods failed to find a suitable rendition.
        Parameters:
        elementId - the id of the element for which to get the rendition.
        size - the size of the requested rendition (ignored if fullSize is specified).
        fullSize - whether or not the full size rendition is requested.
        completionCallback - the block that gets called with the file path in case of success.
        errorCallback - the block that gets called with the error object in case of error.
        callbackHandler - Optional parameter. If not null determines the operation queue completion and error blocks get executed on.
        Returns:
        true if this rendition can be found or generated for the element, otherwise false.

      • getRenditionPathFromCache

        public java.lang.String getRenditionPathFromCache(java.lang.String elementId,
                                                  int size,
                                                  boolean fullSize)
                                           throws AdobeLibraryException
        Gets the path to an element's rendition for a particular size from the local cache. This method will only check the local cache for a rendition of the requested size.
        Parameters:
        elementId - the id of the element for which to get the rendition.
        size - the size of the requested rendition (ignored if fullSize is specified).
        fullSize - whether or not the full size rendition is requested.
        Returns:
        the path if this rendition can be found in the local cache, otherwise null.
        Throws:
        AdobeLibraryException - if error occurs.

      • setRenditionCache

        public boolean setRenditionCache(java.lang.String elementId,
                                 java.lang.String filePath,
                                 int size,
                                 boolean fullSize,
                                 boolean copy)
                          throws AdobeLibraryException
        Sets rendition cache for a particular size using a file path. Use this after changing content to avoid the delay of having the server generate the rendition.
        Parameters:
        elementId - the id of the element for which to set the rendition path.
        size - the size of the given rendition (ignored if fullSize is specified).
        fullSize - whether or not the rendition represented with the path is full size.
        copy - whether or not to copy the rendition from the given path to renditions folder. The rendition won't be copied if this is set to true.
        filePath - the path of the file.
        Returns:
        true if this rendition can be set for the element, otherwise false.
        Throws:
        AdobeLibraryException - if error occurs.

                                 android.graphics.Bitmap image,
                                 boolean fullSize)
                          throws AdobeLibraryException
        Sets rendition cache for a particular size using image data. Use this after changing content to avoid the delay of having the server generate the rendition.
        Parameters:

        fullSize - whether or not the rendition represented with the path is full size.
        image - the image data.
        Returns:

        Throws:
        AdobeLibraryException - if error occurs.
